subject: FedEx Worldwide Express Deliv
body:
FedEx Worldwide Express Delivery Services
Address: 328 Vauxhall Bridge Rd, London SW1V 1AA,
United Kingdom London
Dear Esteem Customer ,
This mail is to inform you of your registered package here. CONTENT:
ATM Card of $950,000.00 USD registered by an Official of the United
Nation. The Fund is a donation to you from the U.N through e-mails
balloting in affiliation with worldbank poverty eradication program.
If interested in receiving your compensation ATM Card kindly reconfirm
your full Name, Address, Contact (Mobile) Phone Number, A copy of your
ID Card or passport. Further information the VAT and COD have been
paid and the only money you will have to pay is the security keeping
fee which is US$88.00 must be paid before shipment .
Be rest assured that your Package has been confirmed valid and true
and delivery will be made once you have meet the necessary
requirements. We are a well established company offering courier and
transport services 24 hours a day for priority delivery of letters,
parcels to any destination by road, air or sea.
Thank you as I'm waiting to hear from you soon with the requested information.
We Be Glad To Serve You More Better .
Sincerely,
Mr. Dennis Stephen.

subject: Re:  FedEx Worldwide Express Deliv
body:
Hello Mr. Dennis Stephen,

Thank you for reaching out to me regarding the registered package. I appreciate the information you have provided. Could you please clarify what exactly is in the ATM card? Also, could you explain more about the worldbank poverty program and how it is related to this donation?

I would also like to know more about your company, Worldwide Express Delivery Services. How long have you been in operation and what other services do you offer apart from courier and transport?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Judy
